ual review.  It is a binary value, 1 for automated and 0 for manual.
Recommendation Type 
The type of recommendation is a categorical variable.  It is a classification 
of the recommendation's purpose.  It is a 3-level classification. 
Type 1:  Security 
Security recommendations are focused on protecting systems 
from security threats. 
Type 2:  Performance 
Performance recommendations are focused on improving 
system performance. 
Type 3:  Operational 
Operational recommendations are focused on improving 
system operational processes.
  
 
